## Components and Interfaces

### 1. Frontend: KYCForm.js (Single-Page Rewrite)

**Current state:** Multi-step form with 4-5 steps, step navigation, per-step API calls.

**New state:** Single-page form with all fields visible, one "Submit KYC" button, one API call.

#### Component Props (unchanged)
```javascript
KYCForm = ({
  onSubmitSuccess, onSubmitError,
  initialEmail, initialPhone, initialFirstName, initialLastName,
  contactMethod, kycId, initialKycData, analystContact, orderId
})
```

#### Form State (simplified)
```javascript
const [formData, setFormData] = useState({
  phoneNumber: initialPhone || '',
  email: initialEmail || '',
  firstName: initialFirstName || '',
  middleName: '',
  lastName: initialLastName || '',
  panNumber: '',
  state: '',
  panCardFile: null,           // File object for PAN card
  panCardS3Key: '',            // S3 key after upload
  addressMatchesPan: true,     // Checkbox: PAN address matches current address
  altAddressProofType: '',     // Alternative document type
  altAddressProofFile: null,   // File object for alt address proof
  altAddressProofS3Key: '',    // S3 key after upload
});
```

#### Validation Rules
| Field | Rule | Error Message |
|-------|------|---------------|
| Phone | `^[6-9]\d{9}$` | "Mobile number must be 10 digits starting with 6-9" |
| Email | `^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$` | "Please enter a valid email address" |
| First Name | Required, `^[A-Za-z\s]+$` | "First name is required" / "Only letters and spaces allowed" |
| Middle Name | Optional, `^[A-Za-z\s]*$` | "Only letters and spaces allowed" |
| Last Name | Required, `^[A-Za-z\s]+$` | "Last name is required" / "Only letters and spaces allowed" |
| PAN | `^[A-Z]{5}[0-9]{4}[A-Z]{1}$` (auto-uppercase) | "PAN must be in format: ABCDE1234F" |
| State | Required (dropdown) | "State selection is required" |
| PAN Card File | Required, JPEG/PNG/PDF, ≤10MB | "ID proof upload is required" / "File must be JPEG, PNG, or PDF under 10MB" |
| Alt Address Proof | Required when `addressMatchesPan` is false | "Alternative address proof is required" |

#### Submission Payload
```typescript
{
  eventType: 'SINGLE_PAGE_KYC_SUBMITTED',
  kycId: string,
  firstName: string,
  middleName?: string,
  lastName: string,
  panNumber: string,
  state: string,
  phoneNumber: string,
  email: string,
  panCardDocumentS3Key: string,
  addressMatchesPan: boolean,
  altAddressProofDocumentType?: string,  // 'UTILITY_BILL' | 'PROPERTY_TAX_RECEIPT' | 'PENSION_PAYMENT_ORDER' | 'EMPLOYER_ACCOMMODATION_LETTER'
  altAddressProofDocumentS3Key?: string,
}
```

