## Data Models

### KYC Metadata (DynamoDB) — No Schema Change

The existing `KycMetadata` DynamoDB table schema is unchanged. The new single-page form populates the same `kycData` nested structure with a subset of fields:

```typescript
// Existing KycMetadata record — populated by single-page form
{
  kycId: "kyc-abc123",
  analystHandle: "analyst-handle",
  analystId: "analyst-id",
  subscriptionId: "sub-plan-001",
  orderId: "order-001",
  userId: "cognito-sub-uuid",
  userEmail: "investor@example.com",
  userPhoneNumber: "+919876543210",
  contactMethod: "mobile",
  status: "IN_REVIEW",
  subStatus: "KYC_RA_VERIFICATION_PENDING",
  lastEventType: "SINGLE_PAGE_KYC_SUBMITTED",
  kycStartTime: "20250115120000",
  lastUpdatedTime: "20250115121500",
  hashKey: "investor@example.com",
  sortKey: "20250115##kyc-abc123",

  kycData: {
    kycId: "kyc-abc123",
    personalInfo: {
      fullName: "Avinash Kumar Singh",    // Constructed from first + middle + last
      panNumber: "ABCDE1234F",
      // All other fields (fatherOrSpouseName, dateOfBirth, gender, etc.) are undefined
    },
    communicationAddress: {
      state: "Maharashtra",
      // All other fields (addressLine1, city, postalCode, etc.) are undefined
    },
    contactInfo: {
      email: "investor@example.com",
      phoneNumber: "9876543210",
    },
    documentInfo: {
      panCardDocumentS3Key: "kyc/pan/kyc-abc123/pan-card.pdf",
      aadhaarCardDocumentS3Key: "kyc/aadhaar/kyc-abc123/address-proof.pdf",  // Alt doc or copy of PAN key
      isAadhaarAddressCurrent: true,   // true = PAN address matches
      addressProofDocumentType: "UTILITY_BILL",  // Only set when address doesn't match
      addressProofDocumentS3Key: "",
    },
    // declarations is undefined for single-page submissions
  }
}
```

### Legacy vs Simplified Record Detection

```typescript
// Heuristic: legacy records have dateOfBirth, gender, or aadhaarNumber populated
function isLegacyKycRecord(kycData: KycData): boolean {
  const pi = kycData?.personalInfo;
  return !!(pi?.dateOfBirth || pi?.gender || pi?.aadhaarNumber);
}
```

